#

Mango Salsa Fish Tacos

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

fishshellfish

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

tacosseafoodhealthyquickeasy

Description

Fresh and zesty fish tacos topped with sweet mango salsa for a tropical twist!

Ingredients

  • white fish (like tilapia or cod): 1 pound
  • small corn tortillas: 8
  • mango: 1, diced
  • red onion: 1/4, diced
  • red bell pepper: 1/2, diced
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime: 1, juiced
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
